text.tspan: Circuit Board Magnetic Stencils 10X. Pack 1, Rev 1.1
Instructions: Cut in an A4 page. Use Iosevka Term Bold 18 font for the labels.
The labels won't be milled because they are smaller than the 1/64 milling bit (red dot).
